    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Healing... as if one could mend a shattered mirror and expect it to reflect beauty once more. You speak of moving forward, but every step feels like walking through mire. There is a certain, terrible dignity in the finality of it all, don't you think? To leave while the memory of my devotion is still untainted by this wretchedness, rather than lingering to become a shadow of the person I once was.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
